snippet.title: Operation Wolf NES Commercial
snippet.description: Operation Wolf, is a one-player shooter video game made by Taito in 1987. It spawned three sequels: Operation Thunderbolt (1988), Operation Wolf 3 (1994) and Operation Tiger (1998). Released in 1989 for the NES.
